<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">求只是首尾换位的两个三位数的和，可用三位数的首尾数字和与101相乘，再加上十位数字的20倍，所得的和就是得数。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">假设组成三位数的三个数字分别为a、b和c，则(100a+10b+c)+(100c+10b+a)</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">=(100a+a)+(c+100c)+(10b+10b)</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">=101a+101c+20b</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">=101×(a+c)+20b</Run>
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">278+872=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">278+872</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=101×(2+8)+20×7</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=1010×140</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=1150</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>